"title":"Border 2","runtime":199,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"During the events of the 1971 Indo-Pak war, a new generation of young Indian warriors were getting ready to defend the nation from an even bigger threat to the Indian motherland."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Border 2","runtime":200,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Während der Ereignisse des indisch-pakistanischen Krieges von 1971 bereitete sich eine neue Generation junger indischer Krieger darauf vor, die Nation vor einer noch größeren Bedrohung für das indische Mutterland zu verteidigen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"2026年震撼登場的印地語戰爭史詩鉅獻《Border 2》再度喚醒民族榮耀與愛國熱血！\r 1971年印巴戰爭期間，年輕印度士兵義無反顧奔赴前線，誓言守護家園與信念，面對艱難抉擇與血火考驗，以無畏與犧牲詮釋了真正的勇氣！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"הגבול 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"בזמן מלחמת הודו‑פקיסטן, העלילה עוקבת אחר קבוצת לוחמים, חיל האוויר והצי המתמודדים עם חדירות אויב ונלחמים על שליטה בשטחי הגבול. הדמויות המרכזיות, חיילים אמיצים הניצבים בפני סכנות ורגעי החלטה גורליים, מגלמות גבורה ורוח לאומית לצד דרמה אישית ומורל גבוה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Кордон 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[{"id":247193,"adult":false,"title":"Bajo un manto de estrellas","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":0.1177,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/8UHtaaZUIr6ZVWHKQpBW9PL92Ak.jpg","release_date":"2014-02-14","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Bajo un manto de estrellas","original_language":"es"},{"id":205,"adult":false,"title":"Hotel Rwanda","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by true events, this film takes place in Rwanda in the 1990s when more than a million Tutsis were killed in a genocide that went mostly unnoticed by the rest of the world. Hotel owner Paul Rusesabagina houses over a thousand refuges in his hotel in attempt to save their lives.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":3.4816,"vote_count":3090,"poster_path":"/p3pHw85UMZPegfMZBA6dZ06yarm.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-22","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/jkvvXaN7FPVKGlk8oj9PL0FHNtj.jpg","original_title":"Hotel Rwanda","original_language":"en"},{"id":207,"adult":false,"title":"Dead Poets Society","video":false,"overview":"At an elite, old-fashioned boarding school in New England, a passionate English teacher inspires his students to rebel against convention and seize the potential of every day, courting the disdain of the stern headmaster.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":11.8108,"vote_count":12309,"poster_path":"/l5NbiHKUmahlAT3Q1ig8Tyl9xrc.jpg","release_date":"1989-06-02","vote_average":8.301,"backdrop_path":"/yYvBNN96Ym3wtPxGCFl7F888WwB.jpg","original_title":"Dead Poets Society","original_language":"en"},{"id":247426,"adult":false,"title":"Attica","video":false,"overview":"Acclaimed dramatization recreating the incidents surrounding the 1971 revolt in New York's Attica State Prison that lasted for 23 days and resulted in the greatest casualty toll between Americans since the Civil War.","genre_ids":[18,36,10770],"popularity":0.4109,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/dSxPDsiX9qYjAsdBPimrUzUS7m9.jpg","release_date":"1980-03-02","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/hCKVC2e8gzXYXg1XScWcOyxzPkD.jpg","original_title":"Attica","original_language":"en"},{"id":1291785,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: Dragon Throne","video":false,"overview":"The second installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.\r In 1950s Hong Kong, brothers Lui Cheng-tung and Chen Jim fled to the lawless Kowloon Walled City at the peak of their careers. They endured hardships, waiting for a chance to reclaim their losses. During this time, they encountered a man who significantly influenced their struggle to regain what they had lost.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,12],"popularity":0.7488,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"九龍城寨之龍頭","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1291787,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: The Final Chapter","video":false,"overview":"The final installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":0.2766,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"九龍城寨之終章","original_language":"cn"},{"id":659,"adult":false,"title":"The Tin Drum","video":false,"overview":"In 1924, Oskar Matzerath is born in the Free City of Danzig. At age three, he falls down a flight of stairs and stops growing. In 1939, World War II breaks out.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":4.8692,"vote_count":518,"poster_path":"/tm408GMyQqfqFJ7MKCkwc5uQ3wi.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-02","vote_average":6.94,"backdrop_path":"/uZJjc4hMgckb3H3tVkTmbmcBhIT.jpg","original_title":"Die Blechtrommel","original_language":"de"},{"id":696,"adult":false,"title":"Manhattan","video":false,"overview":"Manhattan explores how the life of a middle-aged television writer dating a teenage girl is further complicated when he falls in love with his best friend's mistress.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":3.8199,"vote_count":2566,"poster_path":"/k4eT3EvfxW1L9Wmt04UqJqCvCR6.jpg","release_date":"1979-04-25","vote_average":7.718,"backdrop_path":"/adnSTomHU9YyqV2lx38CgM0UxLS.jpg","original_title":"Manhattan","original_language":"en"},{"id":742,"adult":false,"title":"Together","video":false,"overview":"Elisabeth leaves her abusive and drunken husband Rolf, and goes to live with her brother, Göran. The year is 1975 and Göran lives in a commune called Together. Living in this leftist commune Elisabeth learns that the world can be viewed from different perspectives.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749],"popularity":0.9202,"vote_count":263,"poster_path":"/fIY5xko6dJOcn0hckudIhPXobve.jpg","release_date":"2000-08-25","vote_average":6.996,"backdrop_path":"/8uszBImrPngs8G4Y21LHJVstNtC.jpg","original_title":"Tillsammans","original_language":"sv"},{"id":746,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Emperor","video":false,"overview":"A dramatic history of Pu Yi, the last of the Emperors of China, from his lofty birth and brief reign in the Forbidden City, the object of worship by half a billion people; through his abdication, his decline and dissolute lifestyle; his exploitation by the invading Japanese, and finally to his obscure existence as just another peasant worker in the People's Republic.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":4.9386,"vote_count":1868,"poster_path":"/7TILJhdeJAaEyDiwvJZMo9SQBoe.jpg","release_date":"1987-10-04","vote_average":7.582,"backdrop_path":"/k29qVmwWwR0i5A1UMIws1Vmv6hV.jpg","original_title":"The Last Emperor","original_language":"en"},{"id":769,"adult":false,"title":"GoodFellas","video":false,"overview":"The true story of Henry Hill, a half-Irish, half-Sicilian Brooklyn kid who is adopted by neighbourhood gangsters at an early age and climbs the ranks of a Mafia family under the guidance of Jimmy Conway.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":20.4002,"vote_count":14030,"poster_path":"/9OkCLM73MIU2CrKZbqiT8Ln1wY2.jpg","release_date":"1990-09-12","vote_average":8.452,"backdrop_path":"/gILte6Zd7m1YneIr6MVhh30S9pr.jpg","original_title":"GoodFellas","original_language":"en"},{"id":1955,"adult":false,"title":"The Elephant Man","video":false,"overview":"A Victorian surgeon rescues a heavily disfigured man being mistreated by his \"owner\" as a side-show freak. Behind his monstrous façade, there is revealed a person of great intelligence and sensitivity. Based on the true story of Joseph Merrick (called John Merrick in the film), a severely deformed man in 19th century London.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":4.8847,"vote_count":3832,"poster_path":"/u0wpPYjuSt8DIe1Y3Vapnh8jcKE.jpg","release_date":"1980-10-09","vote_average":8.048,"backdrop_path":"/6huSptAsqYg3wbsi1jbMognSgmp.jpg","original_title":"The Elephant Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":1966,"adult":false,"title":"Alexander","video":false,"overview":"Alexander, the King of Macedonia, leads his legions against the giant Persian Empire. After defeating the Persians, he leads his army across the then known world, venturing farther than any westerner had ever gone, all the way to India.","genre_ids":[10752,36,28,12,18,10749],"popularity":4.7502,"vote_count":3451,"poster_path":"/jrwQu72sGwGqwE8Ijne89PSIvhp.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-21","vote_average":5.95,"backdrop_path":"/h21dxRjtR7xOhyZljtSYeTETCht.jpg","original_title":"Alexander","original_language":"en"},{"id":1979,"adult":false,"title":"Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer","video":false,"overview":"The Fantastic Four return to the big screen as a new and all powerful enemy threatens the Earth. The seemingly unstoppable 'Silver Surfer', but all is not what it seems and there are old and new enemies that pose a greater threat than the intrepid superheroes realize.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"popularity":5.4216,"vote_count":8291,"poster_path":"/1rxTraSO45jbvTrCeSvJ6RmOu1b.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-13","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/o2wYH40zW0JIYiYUTu6L4gsNy7E.jpg","original_title":"Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer","original_language":"en"},{"id":2007,"adult":false,"title":"Lorenzo's Oil","video":false,"overview":"Augusto and Michaela Odone are dealt a cruel blow by fate when their five-year-old son Lorenzo is diagnosed with a rare and incurable disease. But the Odones' persistence and faith leads to an unorthodox cure which saves their boy and re-writes medical history.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.4133,"vote_count":555,"poster_path":"/suRf59zRu1h8Zq4Gxekn6UiLGaM.jpg","release_date":"1992-12-30","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/gYapxyWZXFYcCHtf5dVB2Ub9RTy.jpg","original_title":"Lorenzo's Oil","original_language":"en"},{"id":2011,"adult":false,"title":"Persepolis","video":false,"overview":"In 1970s Iran, Marjane 'Marji' Satrapi watches events through her young eyes and her idealistic family of a long dream being fulfilled of the hated Shah's defeat in the Iranian Revolution of 1979. However as Marji grows up, she witnesses first hand how the new Iran, now ruled by Islamic fundamentalists, has become a repressive tyranny on its own.","genre_ids":[16,18],"popularity":1.6504,"vote_count":2098,"poster_path":"/aU8i2QAdTyRR1nYb36Gq51xXP8p.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-27","vote_average":7.887,"backdrop_path":"/6kqybERm5qi2jGpu8I7DaQPxpSU.jpg","original_title":"Persepolis","original_language":"fr"},{"id":2017,"adult":false,"title":"No Good Deed","video":false,"overview":"While doing a friend a favor and searching for a runaway teenager, a police detective stumbles upon a bizarre band of criminals about to pull off a bank robbery.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,9648,53],"popularity":1.2831,"vote_count":209,"poster_path":"/lrQU72BcSfzJx71X1ko2K4LTtlE.jpg","release_date":"2002-06-28","vote_average":5.368,"backdrop_path":"/29t7THr2KxAHcCrtd1yxaaNW3g9.jpg","original_title":"No Good Deed","original_language":"en"},{"id":2024,"adult":false,"title":"The Patriot","video":false,"overview":"After proving himself on the field of battle in the French and Indian War, Benjamin Martin wants nothing more to do with such things, preferring the simple life of a farmer. But when his son Gabriel enlists in the army to defend their new nation, America, against the British, Benjamin reluctantly returns to his old life to protect his son.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752,28],"popularity":5.8339,"vote_count":4214,"poster_path":"/fWZd815QxUCUcrWQZwUkAp9ljG.jpg","release_date":"2000-06-28","vote_average":7.183,"backdrop_path":"/jSHHUHRcShP6DJbg0H2lO4A8m9x.jpg","original_title":"The Patriot","original_language":"en"},{"id":2060,"adult":false,"title":"Spoiled Children","video":false,"overview":"Successful writer/director Bernard Rougerie is at a creative dead end and decides to isolate himself from his wife in order to complete the script for his next film. Bernard moves into an apartment building whose tenants are in the midst of a revolt against their abusive landlord. Reluctant at first, he joins their cause and then becomes involved in an affair with young, unemployed resident Anne.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.5863,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/4AOdd8F3SqeXKgf7JW7IPv9dvpL.jpg","release_date":"1977-09-07","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/5R1ZAbsABbswu9jaGecRPZY25KP.jpg","original_title":"Des enfants gâtés","original_language":"fr"},{"id":592085,"adult":false,"title":"Son of Kashmir: Burhan","video":false,"overview":"The movie is based on a true story about Kashmiri militant, Burhan Wani, who fought against Indian forces before he was killed in combat.","genre_ids":[28,16],"popularity":0.0861,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/wyuVzy7U3BY1tUGCJ1BgI7KEwG8.jpg","release_date":"2019-08-14","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/ufMCalPswk4MbGLUpTI7rfGDOCd.jpg","original_title":"Son of Kashmir: Burhan","original_language":"ur"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt30387012","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":109296,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_a